%SELECTION ===>_ZCMD
%                    ----------------------------------
                     ×     Edit Macro  "SHOWDCB"      ×
                     ----------------------------------
+
    This Edit Macro will write a comment line on the 3rd line of the
    edit display screen with the current DCB information of the
    dataset you are in edit on.

+   The syntax is as follows:

%   SHOWDCB
+
)PROC
     &ZUP = #EMCH
)END
